            <thetext>In current Firefox versions, the scrolling by wheel or toucpad swipe seems to have an effect on both - vertical and horizontal scroll positions.

To reproduce open

http://demo.qooxdoo.org/4.1/demobrowser/#ui~ScrollContainer.html

in Firefox, move your mouse pointer in the scroll container and turn the mouse wheel. You can see that (no matter what wheel direction) the horizontal scrollbar moves to the right, while the vertical scroll works as expected.

http://demo.qooxdoo.org/4.0/demobrowser/#ui~ScrollContainer.html

works fine in Firefox.</thetext>
